{"id": 947, "genre": 1001, "title": "你烦哪些“感情牌”？", "description": "在这个到处都在撒谎撒娇撒泼的世界里，我们讲讲道理好吗？（题图来自：Marion Fayolle）", "record_count": 4701, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607021838431qivpOBTrGbg0who.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-21T11:31:34Z", "options": [{"id": 69632, "content": "要不是为了你，我早就离婚了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 161, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109487}, {"id": 69633, "content": "可是，并没有多少评论?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578635}, {"id": 69635, "content": "如果不是为了你…", "image": null, "praise_count": 314, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493444}, {"id": 69636, "content": "确定删除？是，否。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212665}, {"id": 70404, "content": "亲兄弟明算账\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 582064}, {"id": 69637, "content": "如果不是为了你。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333763}, {"id": 69638, "content": "你要是不吃饭，我也饿着，咱们俩一起饿着。（拜托！我减肥晚上不吃好么！你饿你就自己去吃好么！）", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 479392}, {"id": 69641, "content": "咱们这么熟了说什么谢谢（等等我们熟？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 373655}, {"id": 83209, "content": "亲爱的~帮我投下票嘛~帮我转发求赞求投票~눈_눈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627264}, {"id": 69642, "content": "我觉得我欠你好多…于是你别再付出了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578669}, {"id": 69643, "content": "我会祝福你的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488981}, {"id": 69644, "content": "我是你爸/妈我还能害你不成？【???", "image": "img/option/option/2016070218332767pZxbBXOhIdwUcu.jpg", "praise_count": 181, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274056}, {"id": 69645, "content": "为了孩子别离婚，以后你会感谢我的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 574801}, {"id": 69646, "content": "真的是为你好，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 69647, "content": "还是再考虑考虑吧，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 79375, "content": "各路选秀中出现了功能不完整的人类时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563637}, {"id": 69648, "content": "为了孩子别离婚，以后你会感谢我的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 574801}, {"id": 69649, "content": "我是你爸/妈我还能害你不成【???", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161700M2BpQb7HVyRtgJnW.jpg", "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274056}, {"id": 69650, "content": "谈钱伤感情，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 69906, "content": "我想收藏这次我说??", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430992}, {"id": 69651, "content": "一般人我不告诉ta，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 70164, "content": "  祝愿安好！跨不出的第一步，尘封在自己记忆中。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569536}, {"id": 69654, "content": "亲人你还想讲道理？No way!", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193003R8exzUV3Qbpq4uAj.jpg", "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262394}, {"id": 69655, "content": "我们这么熟，就不要或者就那样嘛??", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450194}, {"id": 69657, "content": "“辅导员是为学生利益服务的呀，同学们可以把我当朋友~”???", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578724}, {"id": 69659, "content": "我可是为了你好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485695}, {"id": 69660, "content": "你很好，是我配不上你?", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578737}, {"id": 70172, "content": "在？我跟他分手了，心情不好。 噢，关我屁事？", "image": "img/option/option/2016060616164228dSCfJmThYQG3qy.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 580265}, {"id": 69662, "content": "我为你付出了那么多", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 69664, "content": "妹子之间上来就喊亲爱的，亲，一副很热络的语气，可我明明跟你不熟也不想理你，这tm真的很尴尬好吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 175, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 73504, "content": "每天都帮可以我投票的，么么哒～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 560595}, {"id": 69665, "content": "你没小孩你不懂。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172009}, {"id": 69666, "content": "公司的人力资源主管跟我们说“有什么问题都可以跟我反应，请把我当好朋友”，真的有人跟他说了之后下一步就去告诉老板了，呵呵呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 70690, "content": "我是为你着想……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583358}, {"id": 69668, "content": "我只在这里和你说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141748}, {"id": 69670, "content": "你要学会感恩 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565354}, {"id": 69671, "content": "他那么喜欢你，你就接受他呗（……无力吐槽）", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 550628}, {"id": 69672, "content": "我失恋了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172009}, {"id": 69673, "content": "诶呀（撒娇脸）你就帮我一下又没什么损失???", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 555264}, {"id": 69674, "content": "好好看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578759}, {"id": 70698, "content": "旁边这个老太太站了这么久，你一个年轻大小伙子，就不知道让一下？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583216}, {"id": 69675, "content": "我们还会害你吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 574991}, {"id": 69676, "content": "求点赞！ 编号#%^#的那个", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578362}, {"id": 70701, "content": "你以后会明白的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581744}, {"id": 69678, "content": "我是为你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68844}, {"id": 69679, "content": "我你，我我你你，我你嘛，你我嘛，你你你，我我我，我…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575329}, {"id": 69681, "content": "人前啥都没问题 背后告诉你我不会", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440375}, {"id": 69684, "content": "我都跟你道歉了你还生气？", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578770}, {"id": 69429, "content": "“主人你真的要卸载我吗”？", "image": null, "praise_count": 970, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 69431, "content": "亲亲……（谁跟你亲", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}]}